	   <tr><td colspan=2>Small race warriors are a waste of space for 2 reasons: lack of stats that matter and slam. One, str and stam are far more important than dex...and while agi is important for dodge, if you have a natural stam less than 100 you are a waste of plate lottos. This isnt my opinion, this is a fact based on real game play vs 50+ mobs. If you have a natural stam over 100 and you run out of energy it makes no real attack difference. If you have less than that and run out, you will be constantly asking healers for zing just to keep agro.<br><br>I cant stress the benefits of shieldless slam enough for a tank! If you are a warrior you WONT want to use a shield.....that would make you a pally without spells! Slam has saved more groups and raids for me than I can count! It disrupts spells, and stuns running mobs when snare isnt available or wont stick. ONLY large races can slam w/o a shield. IMO small race warriors are basically rangers with slightly better AC and no spells or track!<br><br>Zoth<br>&nbsp;<br>Zoth Soulfury<br>Warlord of Mith Marr</td></tr>
